author: Reuters
title: Peru's economy likely grew by at least 3 pct in September -finmin
text:
LIMA Oct 16 Peru's economy likely grew by at least 3 percent in September from the same month a year earlier, the finance minister was Quote: d as saying in the state newspaper on Friday.
Alonso Segura could not immediately be reached to confirm the accuracy of the Quote: s in El Peruano.
Official growth data for September is scheduled for release Nov. 13.
The economy slowed in August from previous months, expanding 2.57 percent on the year.
(Reporting By Mitra Taj; Editing by Meredith Mazzilli)
